
Project Idea : Portal Factory

##  If to create a android app for the designing a portal, It takes a lot of time to design such portals even 
when they have some common features. 
So, we are  creating  a platform wherecan generate customisable portals easily. 
Once the Category of portal is selected, one can upload the necessary details and the portal can be set up automatically. 
For a start, we are making the platform for atleast 5 portals -
- Hostel,
- Mess,
- Courses,
- Students, 
- Library.  

We are  working on the functional  requirements of each portal. 
